verbose_text: In addition, beta adrenoreceptor mediated adrenergic stimulation, cAMP, and NF-kappabeta have also been associated with induction of the release of other mediators of the innate / inflammatory response by macrophages, such as eHsp72, which in turn modulates the innate / inflammatory responses with the participation of beta adrenoreceptors and cAMP [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR - XREF_BIBR], or melatonin [XREF_BIBR].
